lead_paragraph: Quinton Stephens, Adam Smith and Nick Jacobs each scored 16 points and Georgia Tech won its biggest ACC game under fifth-year coach Brian Gregory, a 68-64 upset of No. 4 Virginia on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Georgia Tech Hands No. 4 Virginia Rare 2nd Straight Loss
